 rapid identification of curation need and guides curators in performing their work. We thus expect GeneValidator to greatly accelerate and enhance the work of biocurators and researchers working with recently sequenced genomes.</gtr:description><gtr:id>9AA6820E-A96A-45FD-AA34-D3990BD01D77</gtr:id><gtr:impact>Publication is in prep.</gtr:impact><gtr:openSourceLicense>true</gtr:openSourceLicense><gtr:title>GeneValidator</gtr:title><gtr:type>Software</gtr:type><gtr:url>https://github.com/monicadragan/GeneValidator/</gtr:url><gtr:yearFirstProvided>2014</gtr:yearFirstProvided></gtr:softwareAndTechnicalProductOutput><gtr:softwareAndTechnicalProductOutput><gtr:description>Makes it easier to perform BLAST</gtr:description><gtr:id>11654CA9-446F-4CAA-8489-4BC3289BE0F4</gtr:id><gtr:impact>(development has continued).</gtr:impact><gtr:openSourceLicense>true</gtr:openSourceLicense><gtr:title>Sequenceserver</gtr:title><gtr:type>Software</gtr:type><gtr:url>http://www.sequenceserver.com</gtr:url><gtr:yearFirstProvided>2012</gtr:yearFirstProvided></gtr:softwareAndTechnicalProductOutput></gtr:softwareAndTechnicalProductOutputs><gtr:spinOutOutputs/></gtr:output><gtr:publications><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/DCF1B92C-2531-48E4-8329-635939900E9D"><gtr:id>DCF1B92C-2531-48E4-8329-635939900E9D</gtr:id><gtr:title>Arthropod genomics beyond fruit flies: bridging the gap between proximate and ultimate causation.</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Briefings in functional genomics</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/1bc0d4e6a2eb249cb520c837fad1928a"><gtr:id>1bc0d4e6a2eb249cb520c837fad1928a</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Wurm Y</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2015-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:issn>2041-2649</gtr:issn></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/153B96FA-1DE7-4774-86C1-B84F3B404B5B"><gtr:id>153B96FA-1DE7-4774-86C1-B84F3B404B5B</gtr:id><gtr:title>Transcript